print("First 5 rows:\n", df.head())

df_clean[index_col] = pd.to_numeric(df_clean[index_col], errors='coerce')

# Sort by year

# Subtask-3: Calculate changes

df_sorted['Increase'] = df_sorted[index_col] > df_sorted['Prev_Index']

# Count valid comparisons (exclude first year with no previous data)

}
